    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >系好安全带，飞行员！ 我们的基地位于一个被遗弃的矿业系统环绕的外星球上，这里充满了危险的外星虫子。你的任务是深入这些区域，利用矿业系统收集升级部件，并从外星矿物中提取生物碎片。地图中到处都是正在扩散和等待孵化的外星虫卵，动作要快！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/053a1503a69cea2535dca90f3e4d6d75.avif?t=1771989149\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次探险开始时，地图都会随机生成，充满了外星虫子。细胞不断扩散和进化，一旦触发，虫子将从细胞中爆发，向你发起攻击。这意味着每次探险都充满未知与危险，时刻考验你的反应速度和策略。独特的群体触发机制会带来不同的战斗体验，每次触发都可能改变战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/5543989cf6d905d4f761ad77fa3d7000.poster.avif?t=1771989149\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/5543989cf6d905d4f761ad77fa3d7000.webm?t=1771989149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/5543989cf6d905d4f761ad77fa3d7000.mp4?t=1771989149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/9e4842851f980e5169785b91396ffff6.avif?t=1771989149\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过不同的方式升级每种技能，以最大化它们的潜力。游戏提供14种技能和超过120种独特升级，发现并利用技能和升级之间的独特协同效应，优化你的角色构建。巧妙的技能组合将让你在面对敌人时更具优势！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/a6616291bdabaa84df354017eafd24d3.poster.avif?t=1771989149\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/a6616291bdabaa84df354017eafd24d3.webm?t=1771989149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/a6616291bdabaa84df354017eafd24d3.mp4?t=1771989149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/5cd3cda301248f5f81169df5052ac57c.avif?t=1771989149\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有三个角色，每个角色都有独特的等级任务。你将在三个地图上进行探险，体验七种不同难度，不断挑战自我。你还可以使用8种小工具和19种物品，每种物品都有不同的稀有度和效果，帮助你在战斗中取得优势。面对10种不同类型的敌人，包括两个强大的首领，每种敌人都带来不同的挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/fab26e8abcf69d15376c3112694a2c46.poster.avif?t=1771989149\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/fab26e8abcf69d15376c3112694a2c46.webm?t=1771989149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/fab26e8abcf69d15376c3112694a2c46.mp4?t=1771989149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个充满危险的外星世界中，展现你的智慧与勇气，打破虫群的重重围困，打造属于你的传奇！</p>",
